detailedViolations.description: Background and foreground colors do not have a sufficient contrast ratio.
detailedViolations.help: Low-contrast text is difficult or impossible for many users to read. [Learn how to provide sufficient color contrast](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.9/color-contrast).

nodes.failureSummary: Fix: Background and foreground colors do not have a sufficient contrast ratio.

detailedViolations.description: Heading elements are not in a sequentially-descending order
detailedViolations.help: Properly ordered headings that do not skip levels convey the semantic structure of the page, making it easier to navigate and understand when using assistive technologies. [Learn more about heading order](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.9/heading-order).

nodes.failureSummary: Fix: Heading elements are not in a sequentially-descending order
